    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I'm looking to find a new home for this absolute beauty. It\u2019s been super well-loved and runs like a total dream! It's in really solid shape and is more than ready for all your upcoming adventures\u2014whether it's the daily commute or a fun weekend road trip. It looks great, drives even better, and has plenty of life left in it. You\u2019re going to love getting behind the wheel of this one! Drop me a message if you want to take it for a spin!",
      "price": 32500.0,
